# Mermaid 

## 1.  (Flowchart)

### 

```mermaid
graph TD
    A[] --> B{}
    B -->|| C[1]
    B -->|| D[2]
    C --> E[]
    D --> E
```

awdawdaw
awdwadaw

awdawdwa
awdaw

### 

```mermaid
graph LR
    A[] --> B{}
    B -->|| C[]
    B -->|| D[]
    D --> A
    C --> E[]
```

## 2.  (Sequence Diagram)

### 

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant A as 
    participant B as 
    A->>B: 
    B-->>A: 
```

### 

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 
    participant S as 
    participant P as 
    participant B as 
    U->>S: 
    S->>P: 
    P->>B: 
    B-->>P: 
    P-->>S: 
    S-->>U: 
```

## 3.  (Gantt Chart)

gantt
    title

```

gantt
    title

            :2024-02-25, 15d
    section 
        :2024-03-11, 5d
```

## 4.  (Class Diagram)

### 

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class Animal{
        +String name
        +makeSound()
    }
    class Dog{
        +bark()
    }
    Animal <|-- Dog
```

### 

```mermaid
classDiagram
    class Order{
        +String orderId
        +Date createTime
        +Double amount
        +process()
    }
    class OrderItem{
        +String productId
        +int quantity
        +Double price
    }
    class Product{
        +String productId
        +String name
        +Double price
    }
    Order "1" *-- "many" OrderItem
    OrderItem "1" --> "1" Product
```

### 

```mermaid
stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> 1
    1 --> 2
    2 --> [*]
```

     --> : 
     --> : /
     --> [*]
     --> [*]
```
